keyMappings:
#Insert your preferred key mappings here.

unmap <c-e>
unmap <c-y>

unmap /
map <c-/> enterFindMode

map j scrollLeft
map i scrollUp
map k scrollDown
map h enterInsertMode

map J previousTab
map L nextTab
map I scrollFullPageUp
map K scrollFullPageDown

map U scrollToTop
map D scrollToBottom

map b goBack
map B goForward

unmap m
unmap `
